2009-03-07  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

        * lib/engine/components/ptlib/audiooutput-manager-ptlib.cpp:
        Do not try writing 0 bytes to the soundcard.

2009-03-07  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

        * lib/engine/components/opal/sip-endpoint.cpp:
        Fixed unregistration of accounts. It was impossible to stop an account 
        from trying to register if that specific account was not already 
        registered.

2009-03-07  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

        * src/ekiga.cpp:
        Fixed bug #574366 (Various problems with dual monitors).

