2009-02-03  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

        * lib/engine/components/opal/opal-call.cpp:
        When calling out by double-clicking on a contact in the roster, update
        the url bar with the called uri.

2009-02-03  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

        * lib/engine/components/opal/opal-call.cpp:
        * lib/engine/components/opal/opal-call.h:
        The call setup is now threaded which makes Ekiga GUI finally more
        reactive again. 
        We still keep the main call setup in the main thread, which allows
        cancelling a call before it fails or succeeds.

2009-02-02  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

        * src/gui/main.cpp:
        Cleanups.

