2008-06-02  Matthias Schneider  <ma30002000@yahoo.de>

	* src/gui/main.cpp:
	* lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-core.cpp:
	* lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-core.h:
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-core.cpp:
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-core.h:
	Add debug level 5.
	Allow lower priority threads to catch the mutexes
	in the audio cores by telling the high priority 
	threads to sleep 5 ms before taking it. Now 
	preferences can also be opened during a call
	with decent latency.

