2008-05-18  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/endpoints/sip.h:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/protocol-manager.h:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/call-protocol-manager.h:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/Makefile.am:
