	confusion with other protocol related features.

2008-05-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* lib/engine/gui/gtk-frontend/chat-window-page.cpp:
	Disabled instant messaging for now. Will be fixed tomorrow.

2008-05-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/clients/stun.cpp: Adapted to new API.

2008-05-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* endpoints/sip.h:
	* endpoints/manager.cpp:
	* endpoints/opal-main.cpp:
	* endpoints/h323.cpp:
	* endpoints/manager.h:
	* endpoints/h323.h:
	* endpoints/sip.cpp:
	* endpoints/opal-gmconf-bridge.cpp:
	Changed architecture, a CallManager now uses ProtocolManagers to
	handle actions and settings. Methods that need to be supported by
	all implemented CallManagers and ProtocolManagers are defined in the
	base classes. It is still a work in progress. It will allow to remove
	horrors like GetSIPEndPoint and GetH323EndPoints. The GMManager is now
	a CallManager handling SIP and H323 protocols using the SIP and H323
	ProtocolManagers. Largely unfinished, be patient.

2008-05-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* protocol/skel/protocol-manager.h:
	* protocol/skel/call-core.cpp:
	* protocol/skel/call-core.h:
	* protocol/skel/Makefile.am:
	* protocol/skel/call-manager.h:
	Changed architecture, a CallManager now uses ProtocolManagers to
	handle actions and settings. Methods that need to be supported by
	all implemented CallManagers and ProtocolManagers are defined in the
	base classes. It is still a work in progress.

2008-05-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* ekiga.schemas.in.in:
	Removed minimum jitter buffer key. The buffer should always be
	at a minimal value.

2008-05-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* engine/components/avahi-publisher/avahi-publisher.cpp:
	Fixed crash. Thanks Fabrice for testing.

