2008-04-13  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/endpoints/opal-call.cpp:
	* src/endpoints/opal-call.h:
	* lib/engine/gui/gtk-frontend/call-history-view-gtk.cpp:
	* lib/engine/addressbook/call-history/history-book.h:
	* lib/engine/addressbook/call-history/history-contact.h:
	* lib/engine/addressbook/call-history/history-book.cpp:
	* lib/engine/addressbook/call-history/history-contact.cpp:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/call.h:
	Improved API. Use time_t as return type for the call start time in
	order to allow easier handling in the views. Changed History::Contact
	API in order to get rid of the status parameter, use two additional
	for call duration and start instead, specific to History contacts, as
	they are related to calls. Improved the history view. Added a few
	const and reference passing.

