	* src/endpoints/pcss.cpp:
	* src/endpoints/manager.cpp:
	* src/endpoints/pcss.h:
	* src/endpoints/manager.h:
	* src/endpoints/sip.cpp:
	* src/gui/main.cpp:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/call.h:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/call-core.cpp:
	* lib/engine/protocol/skel/call-core.h:
	Added ringing_call signal and make use of it. The Ringing tone should
	only be played when the remote party answers with a 180 Ringing, and
	not in other cases. That bug was already fixed in 2.0.x and was
	reintroduced later.

