2008-03-30  Matthias Schneider  <ma30002000@yahoo.de>

        * src/Makefile.am:
	* configure.ac: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/ptlib/audioinput-main-ptlib.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/ptlib/audioinput-manager-ptlib.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/ptlib/audioinput-manager-ptlib.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/ptlib/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/ptlib/audioinput-main-ptlib.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/null/audioinput-main-null.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/null/audioinput-manager-null.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/null/audioinput-manager-null.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/null/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/null/audioinput-main-null.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-manager.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-info.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-gmconf-bridge.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-core.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-gmconf-bridge.h: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audioinput/skel/audioinput-core.h: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/ptlib/audiooutput-main-ptlib.h: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/ptlib/audiooutput-manager-ptlib.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/ptlib/audiooutput-manager-ptlib.h: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/ptlib/Makefile.am: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/ptlib/audiooutput-main-ptlib.cpp: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/null/audiooutput-main-null.h: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/null/audiooutput-manager-null.cpp: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/null/audiooutput-manager-null.h: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/null/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/null/audiooutput-main-null.cpp: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-scheduler.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-manager.h: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-info.h: 
	* lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-gmconf-bridge.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-scheduler.h: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/Makefile.am: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-core.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-gmconf-bridge.h: 
        * lib/engine/audiooutput/skel/audiooutput-core.h: 
        * lib/engine/engine.cpp: 
        * lib/engine/Makefile.am: 
        First shot at the audio input and audio output engine. Not activated yet.
        Both cores feature both a PTLIB and a NULL implementation. The NULL device 
        is used for fallback in case a device returns an error. The Audio output core
        makes use of a primary device for interactive audio and a secondary device for
        sound effects. Also, the primary device can be used for sound effects.
        The output core also relies on a scheduler class, which is a thread that schedules 
        sound events and plays them in the background. This scheduler makes use of a sound 
        event queue, to which events can be added or removed in a thread-safe fashion. It also
        schedules recurring sound events like ringing.

2008-03-30  Matthias Schneider  <ma30002000@yahoo.de>

