2007-10-28  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/endpoints/manager.cpp,
	src/endpoints/manager.h,
	src/gui/callbacks.cpp:
	Removed SavePicture method from the Manager. It is not the right place
	for a method allowing to save the current picture in a file. Moreover,
	it was still based on the GDK display and thus broken when GDK
	is not being used.
	Probably some more work for Matthias.

