2007-09-30  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/gui/statusicon.cpp: Show the main window when the statusicon
	is being clicked.

2007-09-30  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/gui/main.cpp: Removed double define of GM_MAIN_WINDOW.

2007-09-30  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/gui/misc.cpp: 
	Recent modifications in PWLIB do not set a name on the 
	main thread anymore. That leads gnomemeeting_threads_enter
	to take the GDK mutex when it is not supposed to be taken.
	Added guard against that. This removes a few unexpected deadlocks
	which magically appeared in the last weeks.

2007-09-30  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/Makefile.am,
	lib/engine/gui/gtk-frontend/Makefile.am:
	Added build of new stuff, removed build of old stuff.

