2007-09-15  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* endpoints/sip.h,
	endpoints/urlhandler.cpp,
	endpoints/pcss.cpp,
	endpoints/manager.cpp,
	endpoints/manager.h,
	endpoints/ekiga.cpp,
	endpoints/ekiga.h,
	endpoints/sip.cpp:
	Removed all occurences of the old GmStatusIcon from all endpoints.
	Moved stuff from descendant endpoints to the manager in order
	to relay signals.
	Make the manager emit signals when there is call event (incoming,
	outgoing, call established, released, ...) and when a message
	has been received.

	* endpoints/callinfo.cpp, src/Makefile.am,
	endpoints/callinfo.h: Added CallInfo classes to describe information
	about a call (duration, remote party name, ...).

