	searchwindow/search-window.cpp:
	Make the GObject a child of GmWindow so that we can save
	its size and position provided a key is given.

2007-08-17  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* lib/gui/gmwindow.cpp, lib/gui/gmwindow.h:
	Extended API, added properties, and cleaned code
	so that we have minimal code in gm_window_new in order
	to be able to create other GObjects deriving from the GmWindow.

2007-08-16  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/endpoints/manager.cpp,
	src/gui/preferences.cpp,
	ekiga.schemas.in.in:
	Fixed handling of max tx and rx bitrates thanks to Matthias
	Schneider <ma30002000 yahoo de>.

2007-08-16  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* lib/gui/gmwindow.c:
	Added possibility to close the window with ESC.

2007-08-16  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* lib/gui/gmwindow.c, lib/gui/gmwindow.h:
	Added a new GmWindow GObject. That object is responsible
	of saving a window size and position to the GmConf database
	in order to restore it at a later stage.

	* lib/gui/Makefile.am, lib/engine/gui/Makefile.am:
	Updated Makefiles accordingly.

2007-08-15  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>
	
	* lib/engine/gui/common/form-dialog-gtk.cpp:
	Fixed mnemonic activation.

