	shipped icons.

	* Makefile.am: Don't install icon in /usr/share/pixmaps
	* lib/gui/gmmenuaddon.c: (gtk_build_menu), (gtk_menu_show_icons),
	  lib/gui/gmmenuaddon.h: Add menu macro that looks in icon theme
	* lib/gui/gmstockicons.c: (gnomemeeting_stock_icons_init),
	  lib/gui/gmstockicons.h: Install builtin icon theme icons
