2007-05-15  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* pixmaps/status-unknown.png, src/endpoints/h323.cpp,
	src/endpoints/manager.h, src/endpoints/sip.h,
	src/endpoints/urlhandler.cpp, src/endpoints/accountshandler.h,
	src/endpoints/urlhandler.h, src/endpoints/pcss.cpp,
	src/endpoints/manager.cpp, src/endpoints/sip.cpp,
	src/endpoints/accountshandler.cpp, src/gui/addressbook.cpp,
	src/gui/preferences.cpp, src/gui/statusicon.h,
	src/gui/config.cpp, src/gui/contacts.cpp, 
	src/gui/accounts.cpp, src/gui/accounts.h,
	src/gui/main.cpp, src/gui/main.h,
	src/gui/statusicon.cpp, lib/gmcontacts/gmcontacts.h,
	ekiga.schemas.in.in:
	Added support for the new subsystem managing subscriptions for presence, 
	message waiting indications, registrations, state publishing,
	message conversations, ...
	Adds/fixes support for RFC3856, RFC3903, RFC3863, RFC3265, ...
	Many improvements over the original SIPInfo code.
	Code contributed by NOVACOM (http://www.novacom.be) thanks to
	EuroWeb (http://www.euroweb.hu).

