2007-05-03  Jan Schampera <jan.schampera@unix.net>
	* ekiga.schemas.in.in, lib/gui/dxwindow.cpp, lib/gui/xvwindow.cpp, 
	src/devices/videooutput_dx.cpp, src/devices/videooutput_gdk.cpp,
	src/devices/videooutput_xv.cpp, src/devices/videooutput_xv.h,
	src/endpoints/manager.cpp, src/endpoints/manager.h, src/gui/main.cpp,
	src/gui/main.h:
	Fixes, addons and extensions for XV/DX from Matthias Schneider:
	- sets a PIP ratio of 1/5 when in FS and 1/3 when not in FS with DX
	  and XV
	- adds a display of sent and received framerate to the stat output
	- adds the possibility to deactive XV and SX via a gconf setting
	- fixes a leak of the GC
	- does not do fallback when PIP in XV output mode failes - simply dont
	  show the PIP
	- disabling of FS mode when in one-way video mode

