	* lib/gui/gmmenuaddon.c lib/gui/gmmenuaddon.h:
	Added possibility to associate a closure to delete the data passed to
	a callback in a menu.

	* src/gui/contacts.cpp src/gui/contacts.h:
	Use the new closure callbacks defined for the menus in order to be able
	to delete the callback data when the handler is disconnected.

	* src/gui/addressbook.cpp:
	Use the shared callbacks for the all menus and call them through a 
	wrapper in order to have only one callback defined for each action.

	* src/gui/main.cpp:
	Use the shared callbacks.

