	* ekiga.schemas.in.in:
	Use payload types in audio codecs list to remember their order.
	Add default key for video codecs list.

	* lib/gui/gmcodecsbox.cpp:
	Use payload types instead of encoding names to save codecs 
	configuration.
	Always enable non "activatable" codecs.

	* src/endpoints/h323.cpp src/endpoints/sip.cpp:
	Remove assumption that media formats can not have empty encoding names.

	* src/endpoints/manager.cpp:
	Fixed possible deadlock with STUN settings. Fixed video support. Added
	back CIF support.

