	Fixed crash when suddenly deactivating a GConf key.

	* src/endpoints/ekiga.cpp: 
	PTRACE video codecs.

	* src/gui/config.cpp src/gui/preferences.cpp:
	Fixed video codecs support and added back CIF support.

