2006-09-05  Damien Sandras  <dsandras@gnome.org>

	* src/gui/preferences.cpp src/gui/preferences.h 
	src/endpoints/manager.cpp src/endpoints/manager.h 
	src/endpoints/h323.cpp src/endpoints/h323.h 
	src/endpoints/sip.cpp src/endpoints/sip.h
	lib/gui/gmcodecsbox.cpp lib/gui/gmcodecsbox.h:
	Initial work to support audio and video codecs as plugins.
	Ported the GmPrefsWindow to use a new GmCodecsBox GOBject. 
	This object is a box containing a codecs list and building 
	it from a list of available codecs and the current configuration. 
	Callbacks are triggered when the codecs list is modified.

